```

String comparison:

> ðŸ’¡ Try changing `"bar"` to `"foo"`. Are the strings equal

```elixir
"foo" == "bar"
```

Strict equality distinguishes integers from floats:

> ðŸ’¡ Try changing `===` to `==`. Does the result change?

```elixir
1 === 1.0
```

Cross-type comparison - strings are greater than numbers:

```elixir
"abc" > 1
```

Atoms are greater than numbers:

> ðŸ’¡ Try changing the atom name.

```elixir
:infinity > 1
```
